## 4. Table Rules

### 4.1 Prefer `ui.table`
- Supports row selection
- Supports custom columns
- Supports click handlers
- Supports highlighting selected rows

### 4.2 If `ui.table` is insufficient ŌåÆ fallback to HTML table
- Wrap in `@ui.refreshable`
- Use `on_click` on row buttons
- Do NOT use hidden JSON bridges (Gradio workaround).

---

## 5. Template Activation Rules

### 5.1 Template activation must run the full pipeline
1. Resolve template_id and template_path  
2. `ensure_exists`  
3. Load TOML  
4. `verify_toml`  
5. If failed ŌåÆ disable input/export/print  
6. If passed ŌåÆ rebuild:
   - `SecureSQLite`
   - `UiProvider`
   - `Template2DB`
   - `ExcelWriter`
7. Compute `input_capacity`
8. Reset `draft`, `session_rows`, `current_instance_index`
9. Refresh all UI sections
10. Switch to tab ŌĆ£ĶŠōÕģźŌĆØ

### 5.2 No fallback demo templates
- Only use `templates/*.xlsx`.

---

## 6. TOML Rules

### 6.1 Saving TOML must rebuild all engines
- cfg
- verify_report
- ui provider
- db
- writer

### 6.2 Saving TOML must reset all input state
- draft
- session_rows
- current_instance_index

### 6.3 UI must NOT compute Excel coordinates
- All coordinate logic belongs to `core_transform.py`.

