## 8. Export / Print Rules

### 8.1 Export path must follow

`exports/{template_id}/{template_id}_{db_suffix}_{YYYYMMDD}_{HHMMSS}.xlsx`

- Create `exports/{template_id}/` when missing.
- After ÕÅ”ÕŁśõĖ║, refresh print-file choices and select the new export.

### 8.2 Print vs download

- Windows: `os.startfile(path, 'print')` after user picks export + print area.
- Non-Windows: `ui.download.file(path)` fallback.
- Print areas from `writer.get_print_areas(exported_path)` only; print logic must not affect TOMLÕ«ÜõĮŹ.

### 8.3 Long operations

- Disable trigger controls during execution (`button.disable()` / `props('loading')`).
